					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1706" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/margarita-kosior-4lQPh65PdlE-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/margarita-kosior-4lQPh65PdlE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/margarita-kosior-4lQPh65PdlE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/margarita-kosior-4lQPh65PdlE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/margarita-kosior-4lQPh65PdlE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/margarita-kosior-4lQPh65PdlE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/margarita-kosior-4lQPh65PdlE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導 最近網路上一起感人的寵物故事引起網友熱烈討論，一位善良女孩在自家附近的地鐵站發 &#8230;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/24/%e5%b0%8f%e7%8b%97%e9%81%ad%e6%8b%8b%e6%a3%84%e5%8e%9f%e5%9c%b0%e8%8b%a6%e5%ae%88%e7%ad%89%e5%80%99%ef%bc%81%e5%96%84%e8%89%af%e5%a5%b3%e5%ad%a9%e4%b8%8d%e5%bf%8d%e9%bb%98%e9%bb%98%e6%84%9f%e5%8c%96/">小狗遭拋棄原地苦守等候！善良女孩不忍默默感化給牠一個溫暖的家 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img width="2560" height="1706" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/margarita-kosior-4lQPh65PdlE-unsplash-scaled.jpg" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/margarita-kosior-4lQPh65PdlE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/margarita-kosior-4lQPh65PdlE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C512&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/margarita-kosior-4lQPh65PdlE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/margarita-kosior-4lQPh65PdlE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1365&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/margarita-kosior-4lQPh65PdlE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=219%2C146&amp;ssl=1 219w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/margarita-kosior-4lQPh65PdlE-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px" /></p>
<p>火報記者 洪瑜蓉 / 綜合報導</p>



<p>最近網路上一起感人的寵物故事引起網友熱烈討論，一位善良女孩在自家附近的地鐵站發現，有一隻無家可歸的小狗徘徊多日，意外得知牠疑似遭到原主人拋棄，因此才不願意離開，最後經過女孩數日的默默感化後，才幫助小狗走出傷痛，終於願意接受全新的家。&nbsp;</p>



<p>據了解，這名女孩之前在自家附近的地鐵出口處，注意到一隻小狗連續多日都蹲在同樣的位置，出自於好奇詢問了當地鄰居，才得知這隻小狗疑似遭到主人拋棄，已經待在那裡至少一個星期，期間幾乎不曾離開。 </p>



<p>女孩與小狗互動後發現牠性情溫和，心生不忍便決定將牠收養，並帶著狗狗去動物醫院檢查，醫師診斷小狗的年紀約六個月大，雖然身體虛弱但並無大礙，只需要補充營養即可。&nbsp;</p>



<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1220" height="879" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/sanela-arsenic-KIpAJz-E8Gc-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1220%2C879&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-231301" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/sanela-arsenic-KIpAJz-E8Gc-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;ssl=1 2560w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/sanela-arsenic-KIpAJz-E8Gc-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=768%2C553&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/sanela-arsenic-KIpAJz-E8Gc-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=1536%2C1106&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/sanela-arsenic-KIpAJz-E8Gc-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=2048%2C1475&amp;ssl=1 2048w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/sanela-arsenic-KIpAJz-E8Gc-unsplash-scaled.jpg?resize=203%2C146&amp;ssl=1 203w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/sanela-arsenic-KIpAJz-E8Gc-unsplash-scaled.jpg?w=2440&amp;ssl=1 2440w" sizes="(max-width: 1220px) 100vw, 1220px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">小狗起初到新家時明顯抗拒，直到最後才成功被女孩給感化，漸漸變得開朗<br>(示意圖/Unsplash)</figcaption></figure>



<p>原以為事情將朝著順利方向發展，卻沒想到小狗一進女孩的家便明顯抗拒，甚至連食物都不碰，甚至趁女孩不注意時，掙脫繩索奔回地鐵口，回到熟悉的地方，彷彿在那裡等待某人歸來。&nbsp;</p>



<p>女孩並沒有放棄，她依然每天到地鐵門口與小狗互動，更請了有養狗的朋友前來，大家一起圍繞著牠說話與安撫情緒，耐心解釋新生活的開始，也許舊的已經離開，但未來還能擁有幸福。&nbsp;</p>



<p>直到這天小狗才似乎理解了什麼，任由女孩們再次將她帶回新家，這次牠不再抗拒，而是開始適應環境、接受照顧，漸漸變得開朗，如今的小狗已經變得活潑有精神，成為女孩生活中最溫暖與不可或缺的一部分。&nbsp;</p>
<p>這篇文章 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw/2025/07/24/%e5%b0%8f%e7%8b%97%e9%81%ad%e6%8b%8b%e6%a3%84%e5%8e%9f%e5%9c%b0%e8%8b%a6%e5%ae%88%e7%ad%89%e5%80%99%ef%bc%81%e5%96%84%e8%89%af%e5%a5%b3%e5%ad%a9%e4%b8%8d%e5%bf%8d%e9%bb%98%e9%bb%98%e6%84%9f%e5%8c%96/">小狗遭拋棄原地苦守等候！善良女孩不忍默默感化給牠一個溫暖的家 </a> 最早出現於 <a href="https://firenews.com.tw">火報</a>。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
